 699:src/main.cpp  ****             // At zero pressure: cutoff = 0.5x pitch (below fundamental, very dark)
 700:src/main.cpp  ****             // At full pressure: cutoff = 0.5x * 2^(6*prs) ‚Äî exponential opening
